profile_summary:
Hisham Thajudheen is a skilled computer science student with a strong foundation in programming languages, including C++, Python, and Assembly. With a keen interest in software development, he has actively contributed to the open-source community through his public repositories, demonstrating his ability to design, develop, and deploy innovative solutions. As a passionate and dedicated individual, Hisham is committed to staying up-to-date with the latest trends and technologies in the field, ensuring his skills remain relevant and effective.

With a growing portfolio of 14 public repositories, Hisham has established himself as a proficient and reliable developer, capable of delivering high-quality solutions. His expertise in C++, Python, and Assembly enables him to tackle complex projects with ease, making him a valuable asset to any team. As a chai enthusiast with a passion for computer science, Hisham brings a unique blend of creativity and technical expertise to the table, positioning himself as a talented and innovative professional in the software development industry.
